PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 27 - which declares the severe spring run-off and the flooding in the province of British Columbia in the spring of 1997, to be of concern to the federal government, and authorizes the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
